help.info:
This bot will analyze your tree (from the Grow A Tree Bot by Limbo Labs) and compare its growth to other trees displayed on the leaderboard.

This bot assumes that there is a single `/tree` message and a single `/top trees` message that everyone uses. If everyone creates their own `/tree` and `/top trees`, the reference messages will have to be updated every time, or old data will be displayed.

Grow A Tree Analyzer is not affiliated with Grow A Tree Bot or Limbo Labs in any way.
help.setup:
To begin analyzing your Tree, first you must set up the reference messages.

1. Reply to your server's `/tree` message with `.settree`.
  • Analyzer will DM you to confirm that the `/tree` message has been set correctly.
2. Now reply to your server's `/top trees` message with `.setranks`.
  • Analyzer will send you a DM to confirm that the `/top trees` message has been set correctly.
3. Now simply run `/compare` where you want your analysis to be visible.
help.permissions: At a minimum, Grow A Tree Analyzer requires permissions to `Send Messages` and `Send Messages in Threads` if applicable. If Analyzer is given permission to `Manage Messages`, the bot will delete the `.settree` and `.setranks` messages to reduce spam.

embeds.footer: Grow A Tree Analyzer is not affiliated with Grow A Tree or Limbo Labs
